=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider block\">ANNUAL EFFICIENCY GAP</span>\n363 |                   <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono font-bold bg-[#00FF9D]/10 text-[#00FF9D] px-1 rounded uppercase tracking-widest\">MODELLED</span>\n364 |                 </div>\n365 |                 <span className=\"text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#00FF9D] block mt-2 font-mono tracking-tight\">\n366 |                   {formatCompactCurrency(expectedGrossSavings)}\n367 |                 </span>\n368 |               </div>\n369 |               <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-4 border-t border-white/5 pt-2\">\n370 |                 Illustrative recouped cost based on expected 85% workforce velocity optimization.\n371 |               </p>\n372 |             </div>\n373 | \n374 |             <div className=\"p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group\">\n375 |               <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#009DFF]/30 to-transparent\" />\n376 |               <div>\n377 |                 <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n378 |                   <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider block\">RECLAIMED ANNUAL CAPACITY</span>\n379 |                   <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono font-bold bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] px-1 rounded uppercase tracking-widest\">MODELLED</span>\n380 |                 </div>\n381 |                 <span className=\"text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#009DFF] block mt-2 font-mono tracking-tight\">\n382 |                   {expectedHoursSaved.toLocaleString()} Hrs\n383 |                 </span>\n384 |               </div>\n385 |               <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-4 border-t border-white/5 pt-2\">\n386 |                 Equivalent full-time hours returned to strategic i